      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BINNAWAY PEARL (1) failed to feature last start after drifting back at this track, but prior to that won easily by 3.5 lengths at Murray Bridge (16.67) beating Daintree Shady in a Grade 4/5 on April 17. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Ready to return to form. LENNY'S HONEY (7) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on her convincing win the start prior, getting around Gawler over 400m in 22.62. Expected to feature on best figures. STORMY DAY (4) goes very well this trip starting 18 times for six wins and nine minors. In the money last time at this track (17.17) in a Invitation, finishing a 0.8 lengths second. Looks one of the chances. ICE AGE (5) warrants respect with the drop in distance.",
